data.description:
This Inviting Sequoia Floorplan has it All! Freshly painted throughout, nice carpet. The front door opens to the
formal living & dining area, showcasing a sweeping stairway with wooden spindle railings that lead to the second floor, bordering the Loft, creating an elegant and open feeling. This fabulous floorplan offers 4 bedrooms, 2 living areas, and 2.5 baths. The Kitchen features an island, breakfast nook with a bay window, tile flooring, an abundance of cabinets & counter spaces, a smooth top range, and a built-in microwave. A picture window with a decorative arch is the focal point of the master suite, with double doors leading to the bathroom with a double vanity, garden tub, and a separate shower. Other amenities include a privacy fence, garage door opener, custom window treatments, upgraded lighting, and ceiling fans. Beautifully landscaped yard with in-ground sprinkler system front, sides, and back. Ready for that lucky buyer
